# EF Version Explainer — API key template.
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. Copy this file to ".env"   ->   cp .env.example .env
#   2. Paste your key next to ONE of the providers below.
#   3. Run as normal (python run_demo.py / streamlit run app.py) — the key loads
#      automatically.
#
# ".env" is git-ignored, so your key is NEVER committed. Do not put real keys in
# this .env.example file.

# --- Google Gemini (preferred if set) ---
GEMINI_API_KEY=
# Optional model override (default: gemini-2.5-flash)
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# --- Anthropic Claude (used only if no Gemini key is set) ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-5
